ProjectInvoiceTaxSummary is a BusinessClass
    owned by Projects
    prefix is PSITS

    Ontology
    	part of ProjectContractInvoice
    		relative key is TaxSummaryKey
    		
	Patterns
		disable Auditing
		disable AuditIndex
		disable EffectiveDated
		disable AsOfDateProcessing
		
    Persistent Fields
        TaxableAmount		is like InternationalAmount
    	TaxAmount			is like InternationalAmount
		TaxRate             is Percent size 7.5

	Transient Fields
		Generating			is Boolean

	Local Fields

	Rule Blocks
		
	Derived Fields
			
    Conditions

    Relations

    Field Rules
			
	Actions
		Create is a Create Action
			restricted
			bypass field rules
		Update is an Update Action
			restricted
			Action Rules
				if  (TaxableAmount = 0
				and !Generating)
					TaxAmount = 0


		Purge is a Purge Action
			restricted

				
				
